                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>&nbsp&nbsp
                        醫院連絡人
                    </div>
                       <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 underLine">
                         ${memSvc.getOneMem(hosVO.hos_MemId).mem_name}
